OL,5, The situation with energy bills is "a  
OL,6, national crisis" on the scale of the   
OL,7, Covid pandemic, Martin Lewis has said. 
OL,9,FThe consumer expert told the BBC       
OL,10,Fsupport needed to double to make up for
OL,11,Fthe huge expected rise in bills.       
OL,13,FThe government said it had "continually
OL,14,Ftaken action to help households".      
OL,16,FIt comes as a survey by comparison site
OL,17,FUswitch suggested many people are      
OL,18,Ffalling behind on energy payments with 
OL,19,Ftotal debt owed three times higher than
OL,20,Fin September last year.                
